-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/indian-navy-plans-to-buy-six-submarines-for-10-7-billion-times-reports.html

          
          
             India plans to acquire six new
submarines at a cost of 500 billion rupees ($10.7 billion) to
strengthen its navy, the Times of India reported, citing an
unidentified source.  
